Explanation of the error from SAP messages :
--------------------------------------------

-3014: Invalid end of SQL statement

Explanation:

According to the syntax, the specified SQL statement is not allowed in the SQLMODE which is currently valid.

User Action:

The error position shows the location where the specified SQL statement deviates from the permitted syntax.

 
Correction :
------------

In the case, on the second SELECT, we have to re-name the columns using AS.

SELECT LogName, LName, FName FROM (SELECT U.ID, U.LoginName AS logName, U.LastName AS LName, U.FirstName AS FName FROM Users  U, UsersGroups  UG, Groups  G WHERE U.ID = UG.Users AND G.Name =  'KR PROG' AND UG.Groups = G.ID) ORDER BY 1;




******************************************************************************
Error 3 : FOR UPDATE
******************************************************************************


What I did:
-----------

In "Reference Data", "sytems References Data", "Platform", save or delete a platform.
 

Error produced :
-----------------

OPEN: SELECT    tabelle, spalte, aktion FROM            REFERENZEN WHERE       referenz = 'Platform' ORDER BY   3 DESC
-- NATIVE SQL: 
SELECT  tabelle, spalte, aktion FROM            REFERENZEN WHERE               referenz = 'Platform' ORDER BY   3 DESC;
--
OPEN: SELECT TS FROM Platform WHERE ID = 3 FOR UPDATE
-- NATIVE SQL: 
SELECT TS FROM Platform WHERE ID = 3 FOR UPDATE;
--
com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.visual.VRuntimeException: SAP DBTech SQL: [-5015] (at 48) Missing keyword:OF
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.visual.VWindow.abortProtected(VWindow.java:572)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VForm.abortProtected(VForm.java:662)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.Commands.deleteBlock(Commands.java:429)
        at com.kopiright.apps.mialy.Platform$VKT_BLOCK_Platform.executeVoidTrigger(Platform.vf:285)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.visual.SActor$1.run(SActor.java:59)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VForm.performActionImpl(VForm.java:525)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VForm.access$0(VForm.java)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VForm$2.run(VForm.java:484)
        at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java)
ORIGINAL ERROR IS:
com.kopiright.xkopi.lib.base.DBUnspecifiedException: SAP DBTech SQL: [-5015] (at 48) Missing keyword:OF
com.kopiright.xkopi.lib.base.DBUnspecifiedException: SAP DBTech SQL: [-5015] (at 48) Missing keyword:OF
        at com.kopiright.xkopi.lib.base.SapDbDriverInterface.convertException(SapDbDriverInterface.java:91)
        at com.kopiright.xkopi.lib.base.Connection.convertException(Connection.java:158)
        at com.kopiright.xkopi.lib.base.Query.open(Query.java:172)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VBlock.deleteRecord(VBlock.java:3225)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.VBlock.delete(VBlock.java:1780)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.form.Commands.deleteBlock(Commands.java:424)
        at com.kopiright.apps.mialy.Platform$VKT_BLOCK_Platform.executeVoidTrigger(Platform.vf:285)
        at com.kopiright.vkopi.lib.visual.SActor$1.run(SActor.java:59)
